{"tid":508187,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"［PC] 新流星搜劍錄 - 正式stream上架！","createTime":"2017-12-24T04:03:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-26T05:55:15.000Z","uid":88126,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"73fa6353bfbc82c672705cbb6cba98b3c6e07e84","tid":508187,"uid":88126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T04:03:45.000Z","msg":"　　保留《流星蝴蝶劍》戰鬥精髓、強調冷兵器格鬥《新流星搜劍錄》於（21）正式登上 Steam 平台。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/24/120331_4f39aab86e8c8b5154c619b86bd64cac.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F24%2F120331_4f39aab86e8c8b5154c619b86bd64cac.jpg&h=231473ee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n　　於 2013 年首次公開的《新流星搜劍錄》是一款保留《流星蝴蝶劍》戰鬥精髓、強調冷兵器格鬥，並加入很多遊戲元素與武器的對戰線上遊戲。本作由單機武俠遊戲《流星蝴蝶劍. net》製作人蔡浚松擔任總監、中國大陸空中網旗下泰坦工作室研發。<br />\n <br />\n　　遊戲將武俠題材與格鬥玩法結合，且擁有獨特的冷兵器，以及由各色兵器演化出的百變連招，玩家可以使用十餘種不同的冷兵器，如劍、棍、匕首等，並搭配不同種類的副手武器，如暗器、弓箭、火銃等。每一種兵器都有自己的特性並且相生相剋，同時還具有各自不同的招式，玩家可以根據喜好選擇並開創自己的戰鬥風格。<br />\n<br />\n <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/24/120241_35e948fbb42cfbc993fa5879038e92e1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F24%2F120241_35e948fbb42cfbc993fa5879038e92e1.jpg&h=ceba4621&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a1cbd524a8310200087ad05bdc7e87244aec4a76","tid":508187,"uid":88126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T04:08:52.000Z","msg":"有冇人玩緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n首4日下載登入仲送紀念時裝<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係時候一齊踏入江湖啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3e1fb9d87c21d4387fa0c2689df3765632a124a","tid":508187,"uid":163101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T07:08:52.000Z","msg":"隻遊戲打擊感如何?"},{"pid":"8f5928cb147b7d654b87d291be36283b34bee7d8","tid":508187,"uid":88126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"c